    "feat": {
        "name": "Venipuncture",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "A shell made up of hundreds of razor-thin needles of blood forms around you before exploding outward, lacerating foes in a 30-foot emanation. The needles deal piercing damage equal to double the number of sanguimancy Hit Points you spent, to a maximum of 80 damage. Creatures caught in the blast must attempt a basic Reflex save. The DC for this save is your class DC or spell DC, whichever is higher.",
        "level": 10,
